- Nationalist theories: 2 papers - Cultural nations and homeland claims (Miller, Meisels)
- Place-based/river model theories: 3 papers - Ecological and relational approaches (Nine, Ochoa Espejo)
- Gentrification and urban applications: 4 papers - Applying territorial rights to neighborhoods
- Phenomenology of place: 2 papers - Foundational work on place and experience (Malpas, Casey)
- Cosmopolitanism vs. localism: 2 papers - Mobility rights and hospitality debates
